## My Obsidian Vault

[After completing Guide 06, fill in your vault path]

**Location:**
- Mac: `/Users/[yourname]/Documents/[VaultName]/`
- Windows: `/mnt/c/Users/[yourname]/Documents/[VaultName]/`

**Structure:**
- `Inbox/` — Quick captures, unprocessed
- `Areas/` — Ongoing responsibilities
- `Projects/` — Active projects
- `Resources/` — Reference material
- `Archive/` — Completed items
- `Daily Notes/` — Daily logs

**Rules:**
- When I say "note this" → add to Inbox/ with today's date as title
- When capturing a meeting → Projects/[project]/Meetings/
- When I ask you to search my notes → check vault before web

